    body(style='word-spacing:normal;background-color:#F4F4F4;')
        div(style='background-color:#F4F4F4;')

            div(style='background-color:#ffffff;margin:40px auto;padding-bottom:40px;max-width:700px;')

                table( cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' role='presentation' style='vertical-align:top;' width='100%')
                    tbody

                        include includes/header

                        tr
                            td(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;')
                                div(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;word-break:break-word;width:85%;margin:50px auto 10px;')
                                    h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 700;text-align:start;')
                                        p(style='color:#000;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:18px;')
                                            | Dear, #{recieverName}
                                    h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 400;text-align:start;flex-wrap:wrap')
                                        p(style='color:#5C5C5C;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:13px;')
                                            | We are pleased to inform you that we have recieved the payment of #{amount}.
                                    h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 400;text-align:start;flex-wrap:wrap')
                                        p(style='color:#5C5C5C;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:13px;')
                                            | Please see thee list of the item(s) that you paid for:

                        tr
                            td(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;')
                                div(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;word-break:break-word;width:85%;margin:10px auto;')
                                    each product in products || []
                                        h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 500;text-align:start;flex-wrap:wrap')
                                            p(style='color:#5C5C5C;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:16px;')
                                                | #{product.name} -  #{product.amount}.


                        tr
                            td(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;')
                                div(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;word-break:break-word;width:85%;margin:20px auto;')
                                    if deliveryFee > 0
                                        h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 600;text-align:start;')
                                            p(style='color:#000;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:16px;')
                                                | Delivery Fee:  #{deliveryFee}
                                    h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 700;text-align:start;')
                                        p(style='color:#000;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:18px;')
                                            | Total:  #{amount}

                        tr
                            td(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;')
                                div(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;word-break:break-word;width:85%;margin:20px auto;')
                                    h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 400;text-align:start;')
                                        p(style='color:#5C5C5C;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:14px;')
                                            | This mail serves as an official reciept for the payment recieved.  
                                    h3(data-testid='kRCGXK-CneANy-XPXRZzv' style='font-weight: 400;text-align:start;')
                                        p(style='color:#5C5C5C;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:14px;')
                                            | If you have any questions, feel free to reply this mail. 


                        tr
                            td(style='align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;')
                                div(style='align-items:center;display:flex;width:85%;margin:20px auto')
                                    p(style='color:#5C5C5C;font-family:Nunito Sans, Helvetica, Nunito Sans, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:20px;font-weight:600;')
                                        | Thanks, EventCircle Team

